主体人工文字/主体人工文字_0039.jpg.mt:
Silk quilts treated with non-elastic weight gain
are more fluffy and elastic!
Friendly reminder:
There are silk quilts on the market with poor fluffiness and elasticity, treated with weight gain.
Silk is sold by weight,
and some unscrupulous merchants illegally use silk floss weight gain treatment.
A 4-pound silk quilt may only contain 3 pounds of silk,
with the remaining 1 pound being lubricating chemical weight gain agents adsorbed on the silk fibers.
Tests have shown that the protein amino acid content is severely below standard.

友情提醒：市场上有蓬松度弹性很差的蚕丝被，有增重处理，蚕丝都是按蚕丝重量卖的，现有不法商家违法使用丝绵增重处理，可能4斤的蚕丝被，只有3斤的蚕丝，余下1斤是吸附在蚕丝纤维上的润滑油性化学增重剂。
经检测，基蛋白质氨基酸含量严重不达标。
